data.description: This beautiful 2-story home is situated on a huge corner lot in the desirable neighborhood of Colorado Springs. It features 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a 3-car garage. The home boasts an elegant interior with dark cabinets and granite countertops and double oven in the kitchen, adding a touch of sophistication to the space. A foyer is conveniently located to the left as you walk in the door and could also serve as an office. Retreat to the loft upstairs for additional living space and relaxation. The master bathroom offers a 5-piece bath with soaking tub and a stand-alone shower, providing a luxurious retreat for relaxation. The laundry is conveniently located upstairs near the bedrooms for ease of use. With AC cooling, you can stay comfortable during the warmer months.    The property’s pride of ownership extends beyond its walls, as evidenced by the well-maintained surroundings and friendly neighbors. It’s an ideal place to call home!    The Cuchares Ranch community is known for its peaceful countryside living and offers all the conveniences of city life with easy access to Peterson SFB, Schreiver SFB, and The Mountain Post – Fort Carson. It is a desirable location for those who prefer a tranquil environment while still being close to major military bases.
